* 政府与政治: '''[[邓小平|邓小平]]''' （{{flagicon|China}}）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www-cgi.cnn.com/ASIANOW/asiaweek/features/aoc/aoc.deng.html |title=ASIAN OF THE CENTURY Politics & Government: Deng Xiaoping (China) |access-date=2017-03-03 |archive-date=2013-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027045648/http://www-cgi.cnn.com/ASIANOW/asiaweek/features/aoc/aoc.deng.html }}</ref>
* 企业与经济: '''[[盛田昭夫|盛田昭夫]]''' （{{flagicon|Japan}}）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www-cgi.cnn.com/ASIANOW/asiaweek/features/aoc/aoc.morita.html |title=ASIAN OF THE CENTURY Business & Economics: Morita Akio (Japan) |access-date=2017-03-03 |archive-date=2013-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027045709/http://www-cgi.cnn.com/ASIANOW/asiaweek/features/aoc/aoc.morita.html }}</ref>
* 艺术、文学与文化: '''[[黑泽明|黑泽明]]''' （{{flagicon|Japan}}）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www-cgi.cnn.com/ASIANOW/asiaweek/features/aoc/aoc.kurosawa.html |title=ASIAN OF THE CENTURY Arts, Literature & Culture: Kurosawa Akira (Japan) |accessdate=2017-03-03 |archive-date=2013-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603092605/http://www-cgi.cnn.com/ASIANOW/asiaweek/features/aoc/aoc.kurosawa.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 科学与技术: '''[[高锟|高锟]]''' （{{flagicon|United States}}/{{flagicon|United Kingdom}}）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www-cgi.cnn.com/ASIANOW/asiaweek/features/aoc/aoc.kao.html |title=ASIAN OF THE CENTURY Science & Technology: Charles K. Kao (China/U.S.) |accessdate=2017-03-03 |archive-date=2002-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20020721015945/http://www-cgi.cnn.com/ASIANOW/asiaweek/features/aoc/aoc.kao.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 道德与精神领袖: '''[[圣雄甘地|圣雄甘地]]''' （{{flagicon|India}}）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www-cgi.cnn.com/ASIANOW/asiaweek/features/aoc/aoc.gandhi.html |title=ASIAN OF THE CENTURY Moral & Spiritual Leadership: Mohandas K. Gandhi (India) |access-date=2017-03-03 |archive-date=2013-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027045653/http://www-cgi.cnn.com/ASIANOW/asiaweek/features/aoc/aoc.gandhi.html }}</ref>

